{"tid":241251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★如果 葛咸城 追擊所有支那股票，支爆會否立即發生？","createTime":"2017-05-13T04:28:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T09:43:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f42c4bf3c34c9f4def622f26c702275307394e3","tid":241251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T04:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 期待"},{"pid":"235a52e5869cef1077346423f829622028284bfe","tid":241251,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T04:29:02.000Z","msg":"支爆近了，好友應當悔改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94130e87e5ddeaec9835a39d8634facd43ee3e8d","tid":241251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T04:31:45.000Z","msg":"瑞聲科技似試水溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n時間剛好一帶一露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17620395f564669fedd92ccd84e3f7f7947483a7","tid":241251,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T04:33:27.000Z","msg":"好似話葛咸城做假<br />\n最新消息係點?"},{"pid":"6db551eca21ae774ddb6fbc28ece6e90f8614c75","tid":241251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T04:34:14.000Z","msg":"batman成世唔做野，一帶一路就開工，相當可疑"},{"pid":"ee3484f61d0392560405559eba57d77912d3d52b","tid":241251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T04:35:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似話葛咸城做假<br />\n最新消息係點?</blockquote><br />\n好似又話人地做假，假中假，但又冇人認頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006559d0fce366c309f34e6355e8987f64fd606f","tid":241251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T05:29:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似話葛咸城做假<br />\n最新消息係點?</blockquote><br />\n文章日期：2017年5月13日<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】就在葛咸城做空瑞聲的同時，該機構竟然也被「火眼金睛」的網民質疑。葛咸城報告中顯示，瑞聲未予披露的關聯公司中，有一家叫連泰精密科技江蘇有限公司，該機構走訪該公司，發現其工廠建築上有「瑞聲科技」字樣，而並非用連泰的名字。工廠提及蘋果是客戶，但它並不在蘋果供應商的名單上。報告又附上一張工廠建築照片佐證。<br />\n<br />\n結果有內地自媒體指該照片為PS（圖像合成），是將「瑞聲科技」四個字PS上了工廠牆上，技術拙劣，字和電纜疊在一起，肉眼就可以看出來。但其後卻有投資者在網上表示，已經到當地看過，照片屬實，並無PS過。記者嘗試聯繫葛咸城查詢，但並無收到回覆。<br />\n<br />\n昨日業績會上，執行董事莫祖權並無明確回應連泰精密和公司的關係，僅讓記者去查年報。公司2016年年報中，11家關聯公司中並無連泰精密的名字。"},{"pid":"eb9c5a38b31085a1831699fc43140c61521a727b","tid":241251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T05:30:29.000Z","msg":"假batman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2708db7480a40c7628cb81585f8fa87f651eaac0","tid":241251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:43:28.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}